{"tid":483341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓國寶李春姬現身 宣布試射「火星-15」成功","createTime":"2017-11-29T04:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T08:03:31.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"13e4ba7e974cb340ef89ffe5bace453f7b2c4242","tid":483341,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"北韓國寶李春姬現身 宣布試射「火星-15」成功<br />\n<br />\n2017-11-29 11:54<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpt08elq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpt08elq.jpg&h=aeba2c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓「國寶主播」李春姬宣布，今天試射的「火星-15」洲際彈道飛彈取得成功，強調性能遠超「火星-14」。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕北韓於當地時間今晨2時，朝日本海發射1枚彈道飛彈，讓朝鮮半島情勢瞬間升溫，中午北韓官媒《朝鮮中央電視台》宣布，試射「火星-15」洲際飛彈獲得成功。<br />\n<br />\n據《朝鮮中央電視台》報導，「國寶主播」李春姬在中央電視台上宣布，今天試射的「火星-15」洲際彈道飛彈取得成功，強調「火星-15」各方面性能都遠超「火星-14」，美國本土已經在打擊的範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n李春姬強調，在最高領導人金正恩的指導下，可以很驕傲的宣布，國家已經實現了成為核武大國的偉大歷史事業；李春姬說，政府發展核武是為了維護國家主權和領土，在美國帝國主義的核威脅下，保障人民的和平生活。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2268064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2268064&d=wpymXzIE9pr1X%2Be76RV4UP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4e00c86c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2268064&h=ea2f8387\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2268064</a>"},{"pid":"f0ad08c7a32ac3d7243facf369feb9a2b171b4b0","tid":483341,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd2d8f8279b6b34b64b363ea3e11d74065910e0","tid":483341,"uid":85659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:56:25.000Z","msg":"2017最佳實業家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">金正恩</span>"},{"pid":"9330135cefa0e70